{"tid":1346411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新界男企唔穩跪晒係地？ 用兩樣架餐食蠔補補佢！","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T04:09:50.000Z","uid":50791,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ae348c9a0c9b1802d44275639b7cf7a40a640649","tid":1346411,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:06:49.000Z","msg":"呢排見大家都好虧，旭d就企唔穩跪係地點得？<br />\n男人梗係要好腰好腎有腰骨，堂堂正正企直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日都講生蠔補身，睇黎大家都要補補佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但出去食蠔就好貴，今日想同大家分享點樣自己買蠔開Party!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點樣揀蠔／買咩蠔好睇自己口味，但另外一樣開Party必不可少就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">生蠔刀</span></span>！自己開蠔食不知幾好玩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n市面上既蠔刀最主要睇佢 <br />\n1. 刀身 <br />\n2. 護手 <br />\n3. 鋼水 <br />\n<br />\n岩岩開始玩自己開蠔既新手最好搵長柄同有護手, 容易借力既刀，始終新手上路啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n刀身就最好搵又長又薄，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">堅硬不鏽鋼單刃刀片，6CM左右就差不多，千其唔好太長，唔係對新</span></span>手而言好難用，會有危險。<br />\n<br />\n個頭要夠尖，先可以輕鬆<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拮入</span></span>蠔殼，而單刃刀片就可以輕易割斷生蠔既閉殼肌，咁樣就食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TiRtrfZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTiRtrfZ.png&h=187a8f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n淘寶個D蠔刀刀身又短又圓，一D都唔好用，圓頭連蠔殼都拮唔入，一Ｄ用都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KstLtuo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKstLtuo.png&h=96df405c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鋼水都好重要，因為開蠔除咗拮入蠔殼，仲要係入面<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉刀</span></span>／撬刀先打得開隻殼，鋼水差撬撬下就會斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要學識用「轉」個道陰力，先唔會斷刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過蠔刀都係刀，始終有危險性，呢個時候你就需要一對手套！<br />\n有人會用普通勞工手套，不過效果非常之差，我建議最差都用防割放滑手套<br />\n<br />\n如果係有筆直既巴打，當然推介<span style=\"font-size: large;\">鋼絲手套</span>！<br />\n外型上似以前中世紀既鱗甲手套，可以防切割，就算<span style=\"font-size: large;\">捉實Ｄ長刀</span>都可以避免被人切手指。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iKEiOus.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiKEiOus.png&h=24efc63e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然啦，唔係盔甲，如果有人拎刀劈你係無可能擋到，咁危險既情況當然係報警求助。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後唔知有無巴打知道邊到有靚蠔買？我聽講新界有Ｄ鋪頭都幾好<br />\n不過呢排成日有雨，大家記得去邊都帶多把長遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後祝大家食蠔順利！"},{"pid":"a0e88a4a597d2e3ee8bbd7852f2269210e1c4998","tid":1346411,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:09:50.000Z","msg":"啊屌，開錯係時事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我原本想開係飲食台"}]}